nmtui - config network interfaces
nmcli - print information about the networks and devices

# nmcli device wifi rescan
# nmcli device wifi list
# nmcli device wifi connect SSID-Name password wireless-password

if you don’t wan’t your password to be stored in the command line history use the –ask parameter like so:
# nmcli –ask device wifi connect SSID-Name password wireless-password

iw manipulate wire less devices and their configuration
# iwlist wlp3s0 scanning



shred - wipe disk
